data.description: Beautiful home situated on 5 private, wooded acres in Golden Gate Estates!  Tucked away from Naples traffic yet close to stores, restaurants and more this home is a standout from others with its distinctive design, metal roof and cupola.   A spanning front porch for rocking sunset evenings and a spacious back lanai for watching the early morning sunrise will make your day! Nature surrounds with no other property in view.  Once inside take in the open great room with gas fireplace, high ceilings and sunlit new impact windows. Light and bright throughout. County records list it as a two bedroom, however two additional flex rooms can be bedrooms just by adding a closet.  New carpet, countertops, light fixtures and freshly painted throughout in 2023.  Plenty of room for a pool, garden, additional outbuilding or whatever calls to you.  Make this one yours.
